{
  "chapter": 56,
  "chapter_summary": "本章承接前文，寇仲与徐子陵在阳武城窦军秘密据点洗去伪装。寇仲察觉刘黑闼对素素有意，私下试探素素心意，素素却因刘黑闼与李大哥同属征战沙场之人而心生恐惧，决心终身不嫁照顾两兄弟。刘黑闼向寇仲坦白对素素的感情，却因宁道奇曾预言他活不过四十一岁而不敢表露。诸葛德威带回巴陵帮可搭船前往江都的消息。三人告别刘黑闼后乘马车至通济渠码头，登上巴陵帮巨舟，意外重遇香玉山。香玉山以酒宴款待，其姐萧大姐亦在场，对寇徐二人殷勤劝酒。萧大姐与香玉山详述宇文阀势力格局：宇文伤一系主江湖，宇文述一系主朝廷，与隋室关系盘根错节。三人意识到此行凶险远超预期，但已骑虎难下。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "原来易容会令人这么难受的，看！我的皮肤都红了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "威哥调出这种敷脸色浆是一流骗人的玩意，但也是一流的恶刑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你看老刘是否对素姐颇有意思呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不是颇有意思，而是非常有意思，他看素姐时，两眼便似放光。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "但看来素姐却像在回避他呢！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "女孩子都是那样子的，愈对你有意，愈装出毫不在乎的样子，好把你耍个半死。更引得你心痒难熬。老刘条件一点不比李大哥差，又懂献殷勤卖乖巧，我才不信素姐不动心。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你想撮合他们吗？不过老刘一年有三百天都去打仗，素姐若嫁了他，岂不是要独守空帏，还得时常担心他回不来呢。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我也想过这个问题，但若嫁的是李大哥，不都是一样吗？最重要是看素姐的心意，让我出去试探她两句。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "素姐！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "进来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "姐姐是否有什么心事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不！没有什么。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "是否在想着刘黑闼那个小子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你在说什么，唉！你想到哪里去了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "你不觉得他对你特别好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不准你多事。你这人最爱胡思乱想，是否厌了姐姐跟着你们呢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "素姐怎会有这想法，我们只是关心你罢了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "刘大哥是个不折不扣的英雄好汉，可是……唉！姐姐不知怎么说了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "那即是说素姐对他印象良好，那有什么不知怎么说的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你是不会明白姐姐心事的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "素姐有事藏在心里不说出来，我又怎能明白呢；看素姐的样子，就教人心痛。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "每趟我看刘黑闼时，就像见到了李大哥，他们都是同一类人，姐姐心中很害怕，这样说你明白了吧？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "姐姐决定了以后好好服待和照顾你们这两个野小子，终身不嫁，以后你们再不要为姐姐的事伤神。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "姐姐不要为自己立下规条，否则将来遇到合心意的人时，亦会因这番说话而错过了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "姐姐有分数的，不用你来教训我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "威大哥到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "现在阳武的水路交通非常紧张，光是有钱也没用，还须有势力才行，大哥现在去了找巴陵帮的人商量，只有他们可吃尽黑白两道，其他帮会都不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你们不是和他们有过节吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "不是有过节，而是有些关系，刘兄听过香玉山这个小子的名字吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不但听过，还有一面之缘，这人是巴陵帮新一辈的著名人物，很懂做生意，在黑白道里颇吃得开，人缘也非常好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这人武功虽稀松平常，却极有谋略，现时杨广最宠幸的两个妃子，一个是萧夫人，一名朱贵儿，据闻朱贵儿便是由香玉山亲自献给那昏君的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "既是如此，为何杨广又派人刺杀巴陵帮的老大呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这些事，是我们这些局外人难以明白的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "刘大哥有打听到什么消息回来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "自然是形势大好，上月李渊于太原起兵作反，李密又连场大捷，杜伏威、辅公佑两人则逞威江淮，我军亦称雄燕赵，隋室现在能保得住的只有西京长安、东都洛阳和杨广龟缩去了的江都扬州。其他地方像我们刻下置身的阳武城，根本没有防御能力，守城将领只是看看该向哪一方投降罢了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "李阀的情况如何呢？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "投靠突厥的走狗，有什么好说的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "有一件事真令人费解，江湖上盛传你们两人知道杨公宝藏的秘密。究竟这是否只是谣传，因为我和夏王曾反覆研究，最后的结论仍是这宝藏只属子虚乌有的传说。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "为何会认为宝藏不存在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当年杨广弑父自立，害死亲兄杨勇，杨素为他出了很多力。那时杨广还披着明君的外衣，对杨素宠幸有加，虽屡次想害死杨素，但表面却毫无痕迹，这是杨素临死前一年的事。故照理杨素不该有谋反之心而暗置宝藏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "宝藏也可以是在文帝杨坚时预备好的，以杨素的老谋深算，该知道功高震主不会有好下场的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "此说或可成立，可是后来杨素之子杨玄感起兵作反，手下连像样点的兵器都没有一把，又常缺乏饷银，则是没有道理。杨素怎会不把宝藏的事告知儿子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "杨玄感作反的地方是黎阳，西京山长水远，说不定来不及把宝藏起出来呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位兄弟确是江湖经验浅薄，几句话就给我套出杨公宝藏位处西京。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "谁想得到刘兄竟会诓我们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "刘兄只是来锻练我们。不过我们只知宝藏在关中，娘不及说出来就过世了，否则说不定会把宝藏送给刘兄。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "有你这句话就够了。说真的，我才不信一个宝藏可有多大作为。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ge_de_wei",
      "speaker_name": "诸葛德威",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚巴陵帮会有一条大船到江都去，为昏君送上各色缕罗绸缎，好让昏君命人剪为花叶，缀于枝头，布于塘上，使他能在冬天看到春夏的美景。我已说好了你们可搭顺风船，巴陵帮今趟真的很给我们面子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这昏君确死到临头仍不知悔改。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "刘兄，我有几句话要向你私下请教。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "有什么事，是否手头桔据？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "我的钱够我们去花夭酒地，刘兄放心。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "我看刘兄对我们素姐有点意思，对吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这种事当然瞒不了你们。真奇怪，我遇过的妞儿不少，但一见到你姐姐便难以自制，唉！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "这是好事，刘兄为何要叹气。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "五年前有人给我看相，说我山根长得太低，两眉煞气又盛，恐怕过不了四十一岁这个关，所以我已打定主意，痛痛快快渡过这四十年的光景就算了，其他事都不敢想。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "江湖术士之言，怎可尽信。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "问题是这个人并非一般江湖术士，而是中原第一高人宁道奇，且是我表明不怕真情，一再央求他才肯说出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "text": "你见过他吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只是匆匆一会，但他那淡泊从容的神态气度，我却到死都不会忘记。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hei_ta",
      "speaker_name": "刘黑闼",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我对令姐的感情，只能深深藏在心底下，不敢负累了她。况且今趟回去，又要转战天下，生死未卜，以后尚不知是否和三位有再见之日，寇兄弟的美意，兄弟心中感激了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_ling_bang_dai",
      "speaker_name": "巴陵帮待",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寇兄、徐兄、素素姑娘，你们好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "原来是香公子！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位大哥切勿怪小弟，我已尽了一切人事打听三位下落，都劳而无功，幸好猜到阳武乃往江都必经之地，故来此等候消息，果然皇天不负有心人，终能与三位再次相会！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "我们也幸好没去找你那个什么佩佩，否则早落到瓦岗军手上。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "香兄真个好介绍。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "竟有此事，哼！若查证属实，兄弟必会以帮规处置叛徒。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "日后遇上事时，我们怎知你不会学佩佩般出卖我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄怎可这么瞧我香玉山，若我有此心，教我不得善终。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "香公子也想不到有这种事的，你们不要再责怪他了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "好吧！但若给我们发觉你在玩手段，我会立即拆伙。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "三位绝对放心，我香玉山绝非卑鄙之徒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "小弟在舱内预备了一席酒菜，特为三位洗尘，素素姑娘请！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "萧大姐是敝帮副帮主萧铣的妹子，一向打点皇宫众妃的日用所需，对宫中形势了若指掌，有她筹谋，今趟字文阀危矣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "果然长得一表人材，难怪玉山一眼便看上两位呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三位请坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "知己知彼，百战不殆。不知两位大哥知否有关宇文阀的事呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "你不告诉我，我怎会知道。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "都是玉山不好，打开始就给了两位公子不良印象。这杯算是我代玉山向两位陪罪好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "若我能象素素姑娘般有两位这么好弟弟，定会开心死啦。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "若我能像寇兄和徐兄般有素素姑娘这么一位姐姐才真好呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "素素怎敢当，我只是个婢子罢了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "无论素素姑娘作过什么身份，在我香玉山心中都是天上的仙女。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宇文阀的事，不若由我来说吧！宇文家最厉害的两个人，就是宇文伤和宇文述，前者潜心武道，与宋阀的天刀宋缺隐为中土宁道奇下的两大高手，武功盖世，却从不涉足官场，生有两子，就是宇文成都和宇文无敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "text": "我还以为宇文化骨是他的儿子，原来不是。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "宇文化骨？真亏你想出来。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宇文述则历任朝廷高位，爵至许国公，位极人臣，生有三子，宇文化及居长，接着是宇文土及、宇文智及。宇文智及虽不入宇文阀四大高手之林，但却数他最高深莫测，我们绝不可轻视了他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宇文伤一系向不任官职，专责江湖中事，而宇文述这三个儿子，宇文化及承袭乃父许国公的爵位，官拜右屯卫将军兼京城总管。次子士及则娶了杨广之女南阳公主为妻，是隋室的驸马爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宇文智及精于木士营造，故作了杨广的少监，江东城北的归雁宫、回流宫、松林宫等“蜀岗十宫”，都是他监督建造的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宇文阀和皇室的关系这么密切，一本帐簿能起什么作用？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "所以我们必须小心策划，否则害他们不成，就轮到我们吃大亏。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 378
    }
  ],
